Concept of token...


Any api tha needs authentication like username and password can be called using "accessToken"
Just add Header
Authorization:Bearer<accessToken>

//=========Get AccessToken

	URL: https://devconnect.lrsus.com/rest/v3/oauth/token
	Method: POST
	Pass Refersh Token instead of access token
	apiKey.id = 3MOMUY5ZQ9FE7N00NU4Q43C9A
	apiKey.secret = anCDOk0/vXpra3XzJIPWYYZILx99JHNBlJ8ZV7QcIa0
	main url => http://localhost:8080/rest/v3/oauth/token?client_id=3MOMUY5ZQ9FE7N00NU4Q43C9A&client_secret=anCDOk0/vXpra3XzJIPWYYZILx99JHNBlJ8ZV7QcIa0&grant_type=client_credentials
get Access token


e.g. Access API that need Username and PAssword with only Access Token

	Url : http://localhost:8080/web/v3/accounts/6955a74b-0140-4cfb-9c1a-82ff6f0e0e23/plan_products
	Headers:
	Authorization :Bearer<Access token e.g. 		
